- Your Highlight on page 111 | location 1690-1692 | Added on Wednesday, 18 October 2017 21:34:43

The problem is that we don’t show up for enough of these experiences. We clearly need them. But it’s vulnerable to lean in to that kind of shared joy and pain. We armor up. We shove our hands into our pockets during the concert or we roll our eyes at the dance or put our headphones on rather than get to know someone on the train.
